Liberation(tm) Fonts — bundled with UnPixel as the default text renderer face.

These fonts (LiberationSans-Regular.ttf, LiberationSans-Bold.ttf) are used because
the Liberation Sans metrics are compatible with Arial, which the original
bishopfox/unredacter renders with — making the port faithful.

